channel.title: I need help! Look!
channel.description: I'm using ddsspeced v3 source and client. And for some reason the server doesn't like connect to my ip. I can use any other server source and client and it works. And other people can get on. But for some reason when I use Ddsspeced it doesn't let others on.

item.title: I need help! Look!
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:

Hosting and playing your server from the same computer = IP: 127.0.0.1
Hosting and playing your server from different computer = IP: youriphere

Easy enough?
